all together there at the end.

187
00:20:18,439 --> 00:20:20,783
And we were pretty much
estranged before that,

188
00:20:20,785 --> 00:20:23,706
so it really wasn't
a huge blow.

189
00:20:23,999 --> 00:20:29,239
But I did love her.

190
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:32,120
And she didn't have
an easy life.

191
00:20:32,171 --> 00:20:35,306
