which I'm sure was just
as pleasant as it sounds.

197
00:20:47,148 --> 00:20:48,680
And then there's my brother.

198
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:50,730
My older brother
had schizophrenia

199
00:20:50,794 --> 00:20:52,060
and when he was 16

200
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,835
